Ian Joll was missing presumed dead after he was forced to crash land his plane on a Dutch beach , but survived to make it home to Gravesend .
When Mabel Joll opened the front door to see her son Ian she fainted , believing she must have seen a ghost .
Sq Ldr Joll had been involved in a strafing attack on German aircraft on May 10 , 1940 .
His medals came to light as his medals and his medals to his medals .